rd change, do not use it elsewhere\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                            \n                            <p style=\"color: #999999; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;\">\n                                If you did not request a password change, please ignore this email. Your password will not be changed.\n                            </p>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                    <!-- Footer -->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;\">\n                            <p style=\"color: #999999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 10px 0;\">\n                                This is an automated email, please do not reply\n                            </p>\n                            <p style=\"color: #999999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;\">\n                                © 2024 Polaris Tools. All rights reserved.\n                            </p>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</body>\n</html>',NULL,'[\"username\", \"code\"]',1,1,'2026-02-03 14:01:21','2026-02-03 20:48:41',0);
